    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>什么是午夜幸存者？</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你来到的世界拥有<strong>长达三万年的自转周期</strong>，<br>这里的居民从未体验过夜晚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你，经历了无数昼夜的午夜幸存者，<br>正是能够守护这个世界、抵挡邪恶浪潮的救世主。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/4b8ee79ddc9f3508ef46c9611963f1f1.poster.avif?t=1764780056\" width=580 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/4b8ee79ddc9f3508ef46c9611963f1f1.webm?t=1764780056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/4b8ee79ddc9f3508ef46c9611963f1f1.mp4?t=1764780056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>战略防线构筑</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >砍树、开采岩石来生成炮塔点，并将木材与石块搬到传送门以转换为资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >预测敌人的行进路线，布置各种炮塔和陷阱，抵御大规模的敌潮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/ea9cc0b1c6be94bbc3fa94da9d6a6e81.poster.avif?t=1764780056\" width=580 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/ea9cc0b1c6be94bbc3fa94da9d6a6e81.webm?t=1764780056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/ea9cc0b1c6be94bbc3fa94da9d6a6e81.mp4?t=1764780056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>过载射击</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人可累积过载能量，能量满时可释放强力范围攻击。<br>通过科技树解锁更多武器与过载技能，在战场中自由使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/92627c1841c36d1bdd030d2d4debf08b.poster.avif?t=1764780056\" width=580 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/92627c1841c36d1bdd030d2d4debf08b.webm?t=1764780056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/92627c1841c36d1bdd030d2d4debf08b.mp4?t=1764780056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>园圃系统</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在农场中种植作物与神器，强化玩家的各项能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理管理有限的资金和田地，保持最佳战斗状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/71f20cdf2bdc653c08e01dc59d5f9e37.poster.avif?t=1764780056\" width=576 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/71f20cdf2bdc653c08e01dc59d5f9e37.webm?t=1764780056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/71f20cdf2bdc653c08e01dc59d5f9e37.mp4?t=1764780056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>技能收集系统</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一波结束后都可以选择一张技能卡用于战斗，通关关卡后可从中永久获得一张。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下一关开始前，选择你拥有的技能卡以获得加成，对抗更强大的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/d3dbdd5bd3409a4b7b0219e583c55fed.poster.avif?t=1764780056\" width=580 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/d3dbdd5bd3409a4b7b0219e583c55fed.webm?t=1764780056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195510/extras/d3dbdd5bd3409a4b7b0219e583c55fed.mp4?t=1764780056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>最后……</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要你曾在夜里睡觉、早上醒来，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你就是午夜幸存者!!!</strong></p>",
